  "title": "Tea Barista",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Responsible for preparing food and beverages, operating the cashier, managing store operations, and delivering quality service to customers while maintaining company standards and a positive work environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare food items following company recipes and hygiene standards to ensure product quality and safety</li><li>Prepare beverages accurately according to menu specifications to meet customer expectations</li><li>Operate the cashier system efficiently to process customer payments and handle transactions accurately</li><li>Manage daily store operations by monitoring inventory, maintaining cleanliness, and ensuring compliance with company policies</li><li>Greet customers enthusiastically and politely, introduce products clearly, and respond to customer inquiries to enhance their experience</li><li>Collaborate with team members to maintain a positive and productive work environment</li><li>Follow company standards and procedures strictly to uphold service quality and operational consistency</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Experience working in the chain catering industry</li><li>Ability to communicate clearly and work effectively within a team</li><li>Awareness of customer service principles to support positive customer interactions</li></ul>",
